been excluded from the total value of Strategic Commercial Contracts above. As of December 31, 2023, the cumulative amount of revenue recognized from Strategic Commercial Contracts was $253.9 million, of which $87.3 million was recognized by us during the fiscal year ended December 31, 2023.
